name: Beau Edwards
text: Very clean everyone was very polite. While waiting to be seated the cook (Tonya) offered to go ahead and prepare my appetizers. Great service....

name: Sue Nichols
text: I've had nothing but rude service from this pizza hut. They even messed up the topping on my pizza once and had the nerve to tell me there was nothing they could do about it. Corporate got a call from me that day. Terrible service for years there. Its nothing new.

name: Madison Troyer
text: Mommy works here. I love the people here and the food is great (;
